        <div id="main">
            <div id="mobile-popup" class="popup hidden">
                <div class="popup-inner" id="popup-inner-android">
                    <h2>CraftOS-PC for Android (Beta)</h2>
                    <p>CraftOS-PC for Android supports all ARM devices, as well as 64-bit Intel devices, running Android 7 Nougat or later.</p>
                    <p>This release of CraftOS-PC for Android is a work-in-progress. Most things should be working, but note that there may be bugs.</p>
                    <p>Note: To re-open the keyboard, pinch anywhere on the screen with two fingers.</p>
                    <p><a href="https://drive.google.com/file/d/1q6KHMofKcyK14vTcTU1Se22hEb2MRqw8/view?usp=sharing">Tap this link to download the APK.</a></p>
                    <p class="cookie-banner-close" style="width: 30pt; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; text-align: center;" onclick="document.getElementById('mobile-popup').classList = 'popup hidden'; document.body.style.overflow = null">OK</p>
                </div>
                <div class="popup-inner" id="popup-inner-ios">
                    <h2>CraftOS-PC for iOS (Beta)</h2>
                    <p>CraftOS-PC for iOS supports all devices running iOS 11 or later, as well as the TestFlight app.</p>
                    <p>This release of CraftOS-PC for iOS is a work-in-progress. Most things should be working, but note that there may be bugs.</p>
                    <p>Note: To re-open the keyboard, pinch inward on the screen with two fingers. Pinch out to close it.</p>
                    <p><a href="https://testflight.apple.com/join/SiuXlijR">Tap this link to join the beta.</a></p>
                    <p class="cookie-banner-close" style="width: 30pt; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; text-align: center;" onclick="document.getElementById('mobile-popup').classList = 'popup hidden'; document.body.style.overflow = null">OK</p>
                </div>
            </div>
